			[li 
				"My first encountered boss is Bomb Torizo, and of course, I escaped :P
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				"The second boss is Spore Spawn (HP=1472, damage=32), killed by 15 Missiles
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				"The 3rt boss is Kraid (HP=4072, damage=48), used Missiles and Super Missiles to kill, charged beams are slow so I didn't use, and it took time to manipulate the monsters to drop Super Missile!
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				"The last boss is Draygon (HP=16384, damage=240) shinespark very helpful with this boss! And to reach to this boss I have to unlock 4 Security Locks
				$LF
			]li
